<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.9.6">
<l>pōtarkaṇ ṭāyiṅkē pōtar kaṇṭāy</l>
<l rend="indent">pōtarē ṉeṉṉātē pōtar kaṇṭāy</l>
<l>ētēṉum colli yacala kattār</l>
<l rend="indent">ētēṉum pēcanāṉ kēṭka maṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>kōtu kalamuṭaik kuṭṭa ṉēyō</l>
<l rend="indent">kuṉṟeṭut tāykuṭa māṭu kūttā</l>
<l>vētap poruḷē yeṉvēṅka ṭavā</l>
<l rend="indent">vittaka ṉiṅkē pōta rāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You know [you should] come!</l>
<l rend="indent">You know [you should] come here!</l>
<l>You know [you should] come</l>
<l rend="indent">without saying “I’m not coming!”</l>
<l>I cannot listen to anything that was said</l>
<l rend="indent">by the neighbours when they say anything.</l>
<l>You’re just a curious kid, arent you?</l>
<l rend="indent">You who raised a mountain!</l>
<l>Dancer who danced with pots!</l>
<l rend="indent">The meaning of the Vedas!</l>
<l>My Vēṅkaṭa [Lord]! Sage! Come here!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
